name: Wealthsimple North America Socially Responsible Index ETF
longDescription: The ETF seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses. The Fund performance of the Solactive Wealthsimple North America Socially Responsible Factor Index, or any successor thereto. It invests primarily in Canadian and U.S. equity securities with the goal of achieving diversified exposure to companies that do not violate commonly held social and environmental values.
